# Copy to .env and set keys for your llm_model (see LiteLLM provider docs).
# Shell variables already set are not overwritten (override=False in monad.py).
#
#   cp .env.example .env

# Examples (uncomment what matches config.yaml llm_model):
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# If stripe_checkout.enabled is true in config.yaml:
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...
